Title: Introduction to C Programming
Details: Learn the basics of C programming language, including syntax, data types, control structures, and functions. Develop foundational skills for software development.

Title: Introduction to Algorithms
Details: Explore fundamental algorithm design techniques and analysis. Cover sorting, searching, dynamic programming, and graph algorithms.

Title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
Details: Learn C++ programming with a focus on Data Structures and Algorithms. Cover OOP, arrays, linked lists, trees, sorting, and searching algorithms.

Title: Basic Data Structures
Details: Explore foundational data structures like arrays, linked lists, stacks, queues, basic algorithms. Learn implementation and usage in programming.

Title: Introduction to OOP Python
Details: Learn object-oriented programming concepts in Python. Cover classes, inheritance, polymorphism, encapsulation, and apply them in practical programming projects..

Title: Software Engineering
Details: This course covers principles, methodologies, and best practices in software development, including requirements analysis, design, testing, and project management.

Title: AWS, Cloud Computing
Details: Explore AWS services, infrastructure, and cloud architecture. Learn to deploy, manage, and optimize applications on the AWS platform.

Title: Database (MySQL)
Details: Learn MySQL database fundamentals, including querying, data manipulation, and database design. Gain practical experience in managing and optimizing MySQL databases.

Title: Problem-Solving Part
Details: Master problem-solving techniques, algorithms, and data structures. Apply critical thinking to tackle coding challenges and optimize solutions.
